title: Ask HN: Did ChatGPT just stop telling stories?
text:
Yesterday ChatGPT would tell funny and entertaining stories when prompted. Now it just says “As an AI model I can’t generate original content or stories.”

Is this just me? I was trying to push its limits and maybe the model stopped playing along.

Show HN: Implement fuzzy search in Emacs using opengpt in 5minutes
text:
I used chatgpt to implement interactive fuzzy search over emacs buffers. It's not perfect but you can see how powerful the automation is with curation.

I spent less than five minutes on this. I am a beginner in emacs lisp. I am familiar with emacs and with search engine design but I am not an expert in either. I would not be able to write this code on my own without consulting a manual and fiddling with it for hours.
